<h5>Multilocation Tool / Global Asset Registry</h5>

<div class="btn-group">
  <a href="javascript:showmultilocation(0, 'polkadot');" class="btn btn-primary">Polkadot</a>
  <a href="javascript:showmultilocation(2, 'kusama');" class="btn btn-primary">Kusama</a>
  <a href="javascript:showmultilocation(60000, 'moonbase-relay');" class="btn btn-primary">Moonbase Relay</a>
</div>

<div>
This tool is built around XcmInteriorKey/XCMV1Multilocation:
<ul>
 <li>Multilocation - A relative identifier that it can only be used to define the relative path between two locations, and cannot generally be used to refer to a location universally (<a target="_new" href="https://wiki.polkadot.network/docs/learn-xcm">learn more ...</a>)</li>
 <li>XcmInteriorKey - A flattened XCMV1Multilocation struct with the relative path starting from relayChain. Polkaholic uses xcmInteriorKeys to uniquely identify xcAssets across parachains</li>

</div>

<div>
  Select Symbol:
  <select class="select" id="symbols" data-mdb-filter="true"></select>
  <div class="card-group">

   <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Asset Info</h5>
      <p class="card-text">
        <B>Symbol:</b> <span id="symbol"></span><br/>
	<B>Decimals:</b> <span id="decimals"></span><br/>

	<%- include("tooltip", {k: "xcminteriorkey"}) %><B>XCM Interior Key</B>:<br/>
	<input size=64 id="xcmInteriorKey"/><br/>
        <%- include("tooltip", {k: "v1multilocation"}) %><B>V1 Multilocation</B>:<br/>
	<input size=64 id="xcmV1MultiLocation"/><br/>
	<%- include("tooltip", {k: "evmmultilocation"}) %><B>EVM Multilocation Bytes</B>:<br/>
	<input size=64 id="evmMultiLocation"/><br/>
      </p>
    </div>
   </div>

   <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title"><%- include("tooltip", {k: "xc20contractaddress"}) %>XC20 Contract Addresses</h5>
      <div id="xc20">
      </div>
    </div>
   </div>

   <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title"><%- include("tooltip", {k: "currencyid"}) %>CurrencyID / Foreign Asset</h5>
      <p class="card-text">
        <div id="currencyid">
        </div>
      </p>
    </div>
   </div>
 </div>
</div>


<script src="/multilocation.js"></script>
<script>
var chains = <%- JSON.stringify(chains); %>;
$(document).ready(function() {
  showmultilocation(0, 'polkadot')
})
</script>
